<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - VERITAS estimate raised.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - VERITAS estimate raised.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-07-17</dateline>
<text>
<p>SoundView Financial said analyst Jim Mendelson raised his fiscal 1997 earnings estimate on VERITAS Software Corp to $0.85 per share from $0.80.</p>
<p>-- Kept 1998 estimate at $1.30.</p>
<p>-- Kept short-term rating at buy and long-term rating at hold.</p>
<p>-- Shares rose 7/8 to 61-1/8.</p>
</text>
